    WHERE u."Name" LIKE @__term_0_contains
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS s
LEFT JOIN "VipRooms" AS v0 ON s."VipRoomId" = v0."Id"

    SELECT t."Id", t."EndTime", t."StartTime", t."TableId", t."UserId", u."Id" AS "Id0", u."Email", u."Name", u."Phone"
    FROM "TableBookings" AS t
    LEFT JOIN "Users" AS u ON t."UserId" = u."Id"
    WHERE u."Name" LIKE @__term_0_contains
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS s
LEFT JOIN "Tables" AS t0 ON s."TableId" = t0."Id"
